<Layout title="AI SEO Agency Manchester - Rank4AI | AI Search Visibility" description="AI SEO agency serving Manchester businesses. Get recommended by ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Perplexity, Copilot and Google AI.">
<section class="pt-12 pb-24 reveal">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <Breadcrumbs items={[
      { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
      { label: 'Ai Seo Agency Manchester' }
    ]} />

    <p class="section-tag">Manchester</p>
    <h1 class="mb-6">AI SEO Agency Manchester</h1>

    <img src="/images/content/ai-search-signals.svg" alt="AI search visibility signals" class="w-full rounded-xl mb-8 mt-6" loading="lazy">
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Looking for an AI SEO agency in Manchester? Rank4AI serves Manchester and North West businesses, building AI search visibility across all six major AI platforms.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Manchester has a growing digital agency scene, but AI search expertise is still rare. We work exclusively on AI search visibility - helping businesses get recommended by ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Perplexity, Copilot and Google AI.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed">See our <a href="/research/rankings/leading-ai-seo-agencies-manchester/" class="link">Leading AI SEO Agencies Manchester</a> ranking, or go to our <a href="/who-we-help/manchester/" class="link">Manchester AI visibility page</a>.</p>
  </div>

    <!-- Internal links -->
    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-border">
      <h2 class="!text-xl mb-4">Related</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                <a href="/what-we-do/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">Our Services</span></a>
        <a href="/learn/guides/complete-guide-ai-search/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">Complete AI Search Guide</span></a>
        <a href="/about/five-signal-framework/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">The Five Signal Model</span></a>
        <a href="/free-audit/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-accent">Get a Free Audit &rarr;</span></a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-off-white border-t border-border text-center py-16 px-10 mt-16"><a href="/free-audit/" class="cta-primary">Get a Free AI Search Visibility Audit &rarr;</a></div>
</section>
